  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education to Protect our Natural Heritage</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">One of Latin America&apos;s most bio-diverse regions and a vital sanctuary for endangered animals, the Sierra Gorda Biosphere Reserve needs ongoing protection. But in an area that is both rich in natural resources and inhabited by impoverished communities, this remains an ongoing struggle. We are therefore investing in the children of the Sierra Gorda, building understanding and respect for nature, and giving them the tools and resources they need to continue to protect their natural heritage.</narrative>
  </description>
